# id: QueryRescorer -> private TopDocs topN(TopDocs in, int topN)
commentText: Returns a new {@link TopDocs} with the topN from the incoming one, or the same TopDocs if the number of hits is already &lt_=_topN.
codeText: private TopDocs topN(TopDocs in, int topN) {_        if (in.totalHits < topN) {_            assert in.scoreDocs.length == in.totalHits__            return in__        }__        ScoreDoc[] subset = new ScoreDoc[topN]__        System.arraycopy(in.scoreDocs, 0, subset, 0, topN)___        return new TopDocs(in.totalHits, subset, in.getMaxScore())__    }

# id: QueryRescorer -> private TopDocs combine(TopDocs in, TopDocs resorted, QueryRescoreContext ctx)
commentText: Modifies incoming TopDocs (in) by replacing the top hits with resorted's hits, and then resorting all hits.
codeText: private TopDocs combine(TopDocs in, TopDocs resorted, QueryRescoreContext ctx) {__        System.arraycopy(resorted.scoreDocs, 0, in.scoreDocs, 0, resorted.scoreDocs.length)__        if (in.scoreDocs.length > resorted.scoreDocs.length) {_            _            _            for(int i=resorted.scoreDocs.length_i<in.scoreDocs.length_i++) {_                _                _                in.scoreDocs[i].score *= ctx.queryWeight()__            }__            _            _            Arrays.sort(in.scoreDocs, SCORE_DOC_COMPARATOR)__        }_        _        in.setMaxScore(in.scoreDocs[0].score)__        return in__    }
